---
/**
 * イントロバナー
 * はじめての方向け導線
 */
---

<div class="intro-banner">
  <div class="intro-banner-inner">
    <span class="intro-banner-label">For Beginners</span>
    <div class="intro-banner-content">
      <div class="intro-banner-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-banner-text">
        <h2>介護・福祉用具がはじめての方へ</h2>
        <p>「どこに相談すれば？」「レンタルと購入どちらが得？」初めての方に向けてわかりやすくご説明します。</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/first" class="btn-intro">
        はじめての方ガイド
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M8.59 16.59L13.17 12 8.59 7.41 10 6l6 6-6 6z" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .intro-banner {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .intro-banner::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: -80px; top: -80px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(74, 144, 217, 0.12);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .intro-banner-inner {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-banner-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    padding: 30px 18px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .intro-banner-content {
    padding: 36px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .intro-banner-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(74, 144, 217, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .intro-banner-text { flex: 1; }

  .intro-banner-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-jp);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .intro-banner-text p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .btn-intro {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }

  .btn-intro:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-dk);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  /* === Responsive === */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .intro-banner-label { display: none; }
    .intro-banner-content { padding: 28px 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .intro-banner-inner { padding: 0 16px; }

    .intro-banner-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 28px 0;
    }

    .intro-banner-icon { display: none; }
  }
</style>
